Biopharmaceutical companies embrace advanced analytics and a single view of Big Data. Disparate data systems, inefficient clinical trials, slow time-to-market, and the lack of operational safety can cost these companies competitive advantage. Thus continuous innovation around data is mission critical. CSL Behring, a global biopharmaceutical leader, understands the benefits of innovating towards a holistic view…


