Get Started with Hortonworks Sandbox










Ready to Get Started?

DOWNLOAD SANDBOX




Overview & Downloads
Tutorials
Resources



 




Hortonworks Sandbox for HDP and HDF is a quick and easy personal desktop environment to get started on learning, exploring, developing, testing and trying out new features. In addition to offering the latest editions of Hadoop sandbox on a VM, Hortonworks also provides a pre-configured Azure sandbox that is available on the Microsoft Azure Marketplace. 
The HDP Sandbox is a single node cluster of Apache Hadoop® and its extended Apache ecosystem.  HDP makes it easy to get started with Apache Hadoop, Apache Spark, Apache Hive, Apache HBase and many more Apache data projects. 
Each Hadoop Sandbox download comes preconfigured with dozens of interactive tutorials, sample data and the most exciting developments from the Apache community. Get up and running in 15 minutes!
The Sandboxes come preconfigured with dozens of interactive tutorials, sample data and the most exciting developments from the Apache community. Get up and running in 15 minutes!
Download HDP Sandbox
Download HDF Sandbox






